    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Without columns or pilasters or without the repetitive use of them in important locations or as influential elements of design; used especially with reference to facades.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sin columnas o pilares o sin el uso reiterativo de ellas en lugares importantes o como elementos preponderantes del diseño; usado especialmente con referencia a fachadas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Zonder zuilen of pilasters of zonder het herhaalde gebruik daarvan op belangrijke locaties of als invloedrijke ontwerpelementen; wordt vooral gebruikt met betrekking tot gevels.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>沒有圓柱或半露方柱 , 或不在重要位置上重複使用他們, 或不以他們為設計的主要元素；尤其用於指稱建築物的正面。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
